claim.claim-text:
A construction machine (10) comprising:
an undercarriage (16);
a superstructure (14) comprising an internal combustion engine (12);
a swivel (15) configured to rotatably mount the superstructure (14) onto the undercarriage (16); and
a fuel system (300) according to any one of claims 8 to 11,
wherein the fuel tank (100; 200) is arranged at the superstructure (14), and the fuel reservoir (190) is arranged at the undercarriage (16).
